description: Case Logic is obsessed with organization! No matter who you are, what toys, tools or technology you have, where you are, or where you are going, Case Logic is your partner in managing the things that matter to you. We are the "stuff wranglers" that make life easier. With this focus in mind, Caselogic introduces the Caselogic ENC-117 17-Inch Laptop Case. Sophisticated styling surrounds a well-padded laptop compartment in each of our EN attaches and briefcases. For those leaning toward a simple solution for school, business or just getting from one place to another, we stay stop right here! Slim, stylish laptop case is well padded, protecting laptops up to 17-inch. High-volume front compartment provides ample storage for power brick and other business or personal essentials. Protective organization pockets within front pocket for valuable electronics. Made from durable Ripstop and 600 denier polyester exterior. 25 Year limited Warranty!
title: Case Logic ENC-117 17-Inch Laptop Case (Black)
